# 4. Combined conceptual-question score

This combined score summarizes only the conceptual-question section: the two choose-strongest-r items and the four coded text responses. It does **not** include value estimation or add-points performance.

```{r combined-conceptual-score}
if (nrow(choose_participant) > 0 && exists("text_participant") && nrow(text_participant) > 0) {
  conceptual_participant <- participant_index |>
    select(participantId, group, lecture_type, practice_type) |>
    left_join(
      choose_participant |>
        select(participantId, group, lecture_type, practice_type, choose_r_pct_correct),
      by = c("participantId", "group", "lecture_type", "practice_type")
    ) |>
    left_join(
      text_participant |>
